OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Feasing this evening to leave some late
OL,7,Fsunny spells, but persisting along
OL,8,Fwestern-facing coasts overnight. Winds
OL,9,Ffalling lighter. A rather chilly
OL,10,Fnight, particularly under prolonged
OL,11,Fclear intervals, with some grass frost
OL,12,Fpossible in northern rural regions.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FBlustery showers return to
OL,15,Fmost areas on Wednesday, with northern
OL,16,Fand eastern areas having the greatest
OL,17,Fchance of hearing some thunder. Some
OL,18,Fpleasant sunny spells but feeling
OL,19,Frather cool overall.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
